claimTokens().details: Allows users to claim tokens once per day

fundFaucet(uint256).details: Allows the owner to fund the faucet with tokens

params.amount: The amount of tokens to add to the faucet

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

remainingClaimableAmount(address).details: Returns the remaining amount a user can claim in total

returns._0: The remaining amount the user can claim

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

timeUntilNextClaim(address).details: Returns the time remaining until the user can claim again

returns._0: The time remaining in seconds, 0 if can claim now

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

withdrawTokens(uint256).details: Allows the owner to withdraw tokens from the faucet in case of emergency

params.amount: The amount of tokens to withdraw
